{"tid":2287734,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內地多市疫情反彈 禁師生離開","createTime":"2020-11-16T04:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T10:58:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"bb3cd7c668be99adff2b38f885eb47cb205a95af","tid":2287734,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T04:08:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201116/O2AS4MQH2VGFBEG7TNMQR5H36Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201116%2FO2AS4MQH2VGFBEG7TNMQR5H36Y%2F&d=fL1pPRntFf1zvvLBqslw3v3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=f1bb2bb8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201116%2FO2AS4MQH2VGFBEG7TNMQR5H36Y%2F&h=7101e5d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201116/O2AS4MQH2VGFBEG7TNMQR5H36Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n內地多市疫情反彈 禁師生離開<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VvbF4EqFkyxHmN_MYHJxnFPWzoc=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5HLTI2OKC5EGZB2AUW3H3VN5LY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVvbF4EqFkyxHmN_MYHJxnFPWzoc%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5HLTI2OKC5EGZB2AUW3H3VN5LY.jpg&h=ad19e64f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■中國武漢肺炎疫情反覆。 互聯網<br />\n<br />\n全國多地出現武漢肺炎本土個案，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「堅決管住人」<br />\n<br />\n全國過去一日（14日）新增13宗境外輸入個案，分別在廣東、雲南、天津和上海等地。早前山東、上海、新疆等地都出現本地個案，黑龍江大興安嶺地區教育局前日發出緊急通知，指疫情呈現反彈趨勢，要求各區各校掌握離開大興安嶺地區的人員行動軌迹，原則上所有教職員工和學生不得離開大興安嶺地區範圍。貴州都勻市亦要求暫停研學旅行等外出活動，各校園要「堅決管住門、管住人」。<br />\n<br />\n全球疫情持續將近一年，上海巿新冠肺炎醫療救治專家組組長張文宏周五在一個論壇表示，中國大陸已有非常好的保護效果，美國疫苗保護率也達到較高水準，大家預期今年年底、明年初有可能迎來一批可以接種疫苗的人，「應該在2022年的春天，說不定我們就可以開始重新背起行囊，到世界各地去走一走。」<br />\n<br />\n澎湃新聞"},{"pid":"5920d274a0855e2d98c45d76bb5d24474c9d19d9","tid":2287734,"uid":221343,"like":4,"dislike":1,"s